Lists of animal and plant species that are [[endangered species|endangered]], [[threatened species|threatened]], rare or uncommon in [[Rabun County, Georgia|Rabun County]], [[Georgia (U.S. state)|Georgia]] are maintained by both the [[United States Fish and Wildlife Service]] <ref> [http://www.fws.gov/athens/endangered/counties/rabun_county.html US Fish & Wildlife Service list for Rabun County] (accessed October 20, 2006) </ref> and the [[Georgia Department of Natural Resources]].<ref> [http://georgiawildlife.dnr.state.ga.us/content/specieslocationbycounty.asp?lstCounty=Rabun Georgia DNR list for Rabun County] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040820104822/http://georgiawildlife.dnr.state.ga.us/content/specieslocationbycounty.asp?lstCounty=Rabun |date=2004-08-20 }} (accessed December 20, 2011) </ref>
